OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F433A1772877887
OL,3,CMan jailed for 17 years after raping
OL,4,Cand assaulting girls at train station
OL,6,FPolice arrest Sonny Boyes on the same
OL,7,Fday of the sexual assaults
OL,9,FA 19-year-old man has been jailed for
OL,10,F17 years after raping and sexually
OL,11,Fassaulting two teenage girls in Exeter.
OL,13,FIn the space of one hour on the
OL,14,Fevening of 9 May last year, Sonny
OL,15,FBoyes assaulted the girls near Digby
OL,16,Fand Sowton train station.
OL,18,FExeter Crown Court heard that Boyes,
OL,19,Fof Commercial Road, Exeter, raped a 16-
OL,20,Fyear-old girl near the station shortly
OL,21,Fbefore 9pm.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/9
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,434,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43302
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F433A1772877887
OL,3,CMan jailed for 17 years after raping
OL,4,Cand assaulting girls at train station
OL,6,FThe victim was able to escape and
OL,7,Fcalled for help.
OL,9,FWhile still hanging around the
OL,10,Fstation, 45 minutes later, Boyes began
OL,11,Ftouching a 17-year-old girl.
OL,13,FThe court heard the 'forceful and
OL,14,Fpersistent' assault continued on the
OL,15,Ftrain. The victim described that she
OL,16,F'loudly told him to stop', in hopes
OL,17,Fthat others would hear.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/9
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,434,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F433A1772877887
OL,3,CMan jailed for 17 years after raping
OL,4,Cand assaulting girls at train station
OL,6,FWhen Boyes left the train at the next
OL,7,Fstop, members of the public and train
OL,8,Fstaff approached the victim, and the
OL,9,Fincident was reported to police.
OL,11,FHe was arrested in Exeter City Centre
OL,12,Fat 10.20pm that evening and taken into
OL,13,Fcustody.
OL,15,FA video released by Devon and Cornwall
OL,16,FPolice shows Boyes being arrested by
OL,17,Fpolice officers.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/9
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,434,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F433A1772877887
OL,3,CMan jailed for 17 years after raping
OL,4,Cand assaulting girls at train station
OL,6,FFollowing a trial, a jury found Boyes
OL,7,Fguilty of nine sexual offences,
OL,8,Fincluding two counts of rape. He was
OL,9,Falso found not guilty of one count of
OL,10,Frape.
OL,12,FA judge jailed him for 17 years,
OL,13,Fdescribed him as having "breathless
OL,14,Farrogance and distorted thinking".
OL,16,FHe will sign the sex offenders
OL,17,Fregister for life and be subject to an
OL,18,Findeterminate sexual harm prevention
OL,19,Forder.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/9
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,434,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43305
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F433A1772877887
OL,3,CMan jailed for 17 years after raping
OL,4,Cand assaulting girls at train station
OL,6,FThe judge said that Boyes had "charmed
OL,7,Fand alarmed" the victims; that
OL,8,Fthroughout the criminal justice
OL,9,Fprocess Boyes had demonstrated
OL,10,Fmisogynistic views; and even while in
OL,11,Fcustody had continued to show
OL,12,Fderogatory behaviour towards females
OL,13,Fhe had encountered.
OL,15,FDetective Constable Jordan Pearce
OL,16,Fsaid: "We welcome the sentence handed
OL,17,Fdown by the court today, which
OL,18,Fhighlights the seriousness of the
OL,19,Foffences committed by Sonny Boyes.
OL,26,@xD@GOU
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/9
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,434,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43306
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F433A1772877887
OL,3,CMan jailed for 17 years after raping
OL,4,Cand assaulting girls at train station
OL,6,F"My utmost thanks and praise are
OL,7,Fforemost with the two victims.
OL,9,F"This outcome would not have been
OL,10,Fpossible without the continuous
OL,11,Fcourage shown by the victims.
OL,13,F"They have both been through a
OL,14,Fhorrific ordeal that no person should
OL,15,Fever be subjected to and have
OL,16,Fcontinued to show incredible bravery
OL,17,Fthroughout.
OL,26,@nD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/9
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,434,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43307
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F433A1772877887
OL,3,CMan jailed for 17 years after raping
OL,4,Cand assaulting girls at train station
OL,6,F"The crimes committed by Boyes on the
OL,7,F9 May 2025 have had a lasting impact
OL,8,Fon the victims, and the local
OL,9,Fcommunity.
OL,11,F"He preyed on two young women, where
OL,12,Fhe displayed aggressive and sexually
OL,13,Fharassing behaviour towards them. He
OL,14,Fwas forceful and persistent in his
OL,15,Fattack committing two separate attacks
OL,16,Fin a very short period of time.
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/9
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,434,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43308
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F433A1772877887
OL,3,CMan jailed for 17 years after raping
OL,4,Cand assaulting girls at train station
OL,6,F"He has shown no remorse for his
OL,7,Factions throughout the investigation
OL,8,Fand during interview he was derogatory
OL,9,Fand sexist, where he admitted to
OL,10,Fengaging in sexual activity with the
OL,11,Fvictims."
OL,13,FDC Pearce added: "I would also like to
OL,14,Fthe thank all witnesses that came
OL,15,Fforward to give evidence - this was
OL,16,Fkey in achieving a positive result in
OL,17,Fcourt today.
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@IO]uD@ROU
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/9
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,434,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43309
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F433A1772877887
OL,3,CMan jailed for 17 years after raping
OL,4,Cand assaulting girls at train station
OL,6,F"I am grateful to the members of
OL,7,Fpublic who acted fast to report these
OL,8,Fincidents to us so we could prevent
OL,9,Ffurther harm.
OL,11,F"As a result of these reports, Boyes
OL,12,Fwas detained incredibly quickly and
OL,13,Ftaken into custody where he was
OL,14,Finterviewed and later charged."
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G9/9
